ING (0/4) |\n\n**Overall: The implementation is approximately 25-30% compliant with the spec.** It provides basic CRUD operations for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter via a custom in-memory store, but lacks the standard Kubernetes client-go patterns (REST client, scheme, discovery, proper fake clients, informers with full factory support, expansion hooks, and proper file organization).\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_2882a6cfdffeU4nObNSroEzGa3","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Verify client-go implementation","time":{"start":1775831978751,"end":1775832157287}}}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775832157339,"sessionID":"ses_2882b03e5ffe0qgNxH0zdvDDhW","part":{"id":"prt_d77d84c6900164XUB7DOTnpe5A","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d77d56097001KKQTYmjKkXC0ej","sessionID":"ses_2882b03e5ffe0qgNxH0zdvDDhW","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":30358,"input":29710,"output":549,"reasoning":99,"cache":{"write":0,"read":0}},"cost":0.009269808}}
